ull,"display_name_styles":null,"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"content":"Hey man, it sounds like you're worried about the announcement I made yesterday about Respondus basically not running on slower hardware, but don't worry, the RDTSC attacks that I mentioned can be emulated, meaning that you won't need good hardware at all.\n\nAlso, which CPU are you running, if you are running an AMD cpu, then we have a fix coming out today that is going to improve performance massively for AMD cpu's. If you're running an older Intel CPU, this update switches from the Broadwell range to the Westmere range, which also improves performance on older Intel CPU's.","timestamp":"2025-09-13T10:26:56.182000+00:00","edited_timestamp":"2025-09-13T10:29:13.568000+00:00","tts":false,"mention_everyone":false,"mentions":[],"attachments":[],"embeds":[],"pinned":false,"type":0,"flags":0,"components":[],"position":0,"userName":"bizarro12345"},{"id":"1416233874450681916","channel_id":"1416233874450681916","author":{"id":"456444425992798208","username":"coronanebulam31","avatar":"f187b2a7adc6d094773abad39f80beea","discriminator":"0","public_flags":0,"flags":0,"banner":null,"accent_color":null,"global_name":"dumbfuckjuice🧃","avatar_decoration_data":null,"collectibles":null,"display_name_styles":null,"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"content":"Hi, I genuinely really like what you are doing. But I bought evadus+ the other day for $120 and then the new announcement came out saying that you have to have good hardware. I was working on it last night and it is so laggy. At no fault of evadus, my laptop just isn't great and I'm not in a financial position to buy a new one especially after buying evadus+. If the answer is no I'll take that, but maybe could I have membership transfered to someone who could actually utilize the platform. Sorry if this is silly I just figured I could ask and the worst answer I could hear would be no.","timestamp":"2025-09-13T01:27:4